rows.label: qst700901_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, it's you. You've been quite
active lately, haven't you?

rows.label: qst700901_msg0002
rows.name:
You helped my brother the other day,
too. As a resident, let me thank
you again. Thank you very much.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0003
rows.name:
So... it's a bit shameless of me to ask, but
would you listen to my story too? There's
something that's been bothering me lately.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0004
rows.name:
In the forest over there, lately "it"
has been appearing. ...And don't ask
me what "it" is, that's just rude.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0005
rows.name:
I thought, "no way," but the other
day I finally made eye contact. I
want you to go check it out.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm the only one on duty here
now, so I can't leave my
post. Could I ask you to?

rows.label: qst700901_msg0007
rows.name:
If you check the entrance to the
forest, I think you'll find something.
I'm sure someone was there.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0101
rows.name:
I'm sure someone was at the entrance
to the forest. I'd be happy if you
could look for any traces or clues.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0102
rows.name:
I'm the only one on duty here now,
right? I can't leave my post... I'm
sorry for the sudden request.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0103
rows.name:
I just have to find out what's
bothering me. It'll be too
late if something happens.
